{"tid":1919894,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"階下囚細哨不改招牌笑容 一代球王被禁出戰監獄足球賽","createTime":"2020-03-11T05:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T15:29:54.000Z","uid":36494,"like":13,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"09f189488eea8b2dc20bc27a8c7b1c88c097ebcb","tid":1919894,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:45:26.000Z","msg":"一代球王朗拿甸奴近日惹上官非，他和兄長涉嫌以假護照入境巴拉圭，現時在監獄還押。不過他的心情未有受影響，今日流出他在監獄中的近照，面上仍然掛上昔日的招牌笑容，似乎對官司甚為樂觀。不過，外媒報導，巴拉圭法院拒絕細哨的保釋申請，他可能要在當地還押數月，當局更禁止他在監獄內踢球，令細哨不能成為監獄球王，在囚友面前展現腳法。<br />\n<br />\n朗拿甸奴上星期因為使用假護照入境巴拉圭，被巴拉圭當局扣留，由於他人氣高企，因此還押首都亞松森（Asunci&oacute;n）的警察總部，而非一般的監獄。不過，<span style=\"color: red;\">由於細哨人氣太強，逮捕他的警察和檢察人員都放下專業，慕名和這位一代球王合照，而細哨亦有求必應，展現陽光的笑容，更擺下「蒲士」，充當親善大使。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\ngloboesportecom<br />\n✔<br />\n@globoesportecom<br />\n Sob os olhares de Ronaldinho, pres&iacute;dio no Paraguai inicia campeonato na segunda-feira <br />\n<br />\n&quot;A gente n&atilde;o espera que o Ronaldinho participe, mas gostar&iacute;amos que ele assistisse&quot;<br />\n<br />\n➡️ <a href=\"http://glo.bo/2PVQw9Z\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fglo.bo%2F2PVQw9Z&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPWCvuqnjOb%2FiGpmC2gL%2Fng4%3D&h=511c5377\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://glo.bo/2PVQw9Z</a> <br />\nView image on Twitter<br />\n<br />\n4,175<br />\n1:04 AM - Mar 9, 2020<br />\nTwitter Ads info and privacy<br />\n<br />\n707 people are talking about this<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更加有趣的是，<span style=\"color: red;\">朗拿甸奴還押的監獄即將舉辦室內足球賽，屆時194名犯人將會分成十隊作賽。不過，由於朗拿甸奴在監獄內無人不曉，監獄方面為安全起見，將不批准細哨參賽</span>，只是容許他觀看其中一場球賽，令這位世界足球先生和世界盃冠軍得主無法將足球足跡踏進監獄內。"},{"pid":"df269ec619bc85466eb4dde76f0d532f36045dcb","tid":1919894,"uid":36494,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:48:29.000Z","msg":"太出名就唔俾參加比賽，好唔公平"},{"pid":"f680fca23f7430861265bf7f5cb1db3795c61454","tid":1919894,"uid":175659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"諗起千王之王2000"},{"pid":"f1fcfa094dd96f482c4bd4de6be2c0949760b84b","tid":1919894,"uid":2054,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pics.me.me/ea-the-only-guy-whose-smile-can-turn-a-red-37214715.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpics.me.me%2Fea-the-only-guy-whose-smile-can-turn-a-red-37214715.png&h=5623cc04&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c41dd2e72da73891e1567347b596c25638193837","tid":1919894,"uid":33868,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點解入獄都咁好笑"},{"pid":"24f2b144f301ebcd98dc68ceea34979533f3b202","tid":1919894,"uid":134087,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:54:46.000Z","msg":"佢落場一個扭曬對面加自己友都得"},{"pid":"e3bc171d7bff1e33e46292dda02e752b4fff78f9","tid":1919894,"uid":123848,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:59:13.000Z","msg":"其實會唔會特登入去踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992703fd5dd9c17c49810b7ae24d07215a015f12","tid":1919894,"uid":66365,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:59:18.000Z","msg":"球王都要用假護照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2542695d81c8d574c06f51f646394624684c3f60","tid":1919894,"uid":155902,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"拎埋監獄盃就真係正式登基成為史一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91d2dceb97dfc9b51e3d9ec5d95084d4c56ac631","tid":1919894,"uid":70110,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2542695d81c8d574c06f51f646394624684c3f60","tid":1919894,"uid":155902,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":2,